Barbecued Chicken
=================

Ingredients:
------------

- 1/2 cup water
- 1 cup vinegar
- 1/2 cup butter or margarine
- 2 tbsp salt

Preparation:
------------

Combine all ingredients in a saucepan. Bring to a boil. Baste each time
chicken is turned until done.

Yield:
------

Mixture will baste 5 lbs of chicken.

